name: Love Tree - 8x10 Art Print
description:
**About This Print**
One of my newest favorites! This print features a tree made of candy colored stripes with magenta, cornflower blue and maroon hearts for flowers!

**Size**
Image size is 8x10 inches centered on an 8.5x11 piece of paper, leaving a white border for easy framing.

**Paper**
- Your print will be printed with archival quality inks on 100% rag 190gsm acid-free (archival) paper.

**Shipping**
- Your print will be safely shipped in a rigid envelope. 
- Please allow up to two weeks for delivery. Print will be shipped within 3 days of payment.

**Special Options**
- Need a different color scheme? Contact me and I can create a custom print for you.

- Need a different size? Let me know what size you are looking for! 

**Additional Information**
- Please note that colors can vary from the ones you see on your screen.
- Please do not use image in any way without permission.
- PA residents will be charged necessary sales tax as required.
